sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant System as System
    participant Media as Media Service

    User->>System: Upload file (image/video/document)
    System->>Media: Send file for processing
    Media-->>System: Return file preview
    System-->>User: Display file preview

    User->>System: Send file
    System->>Media: Store file
    Media-->>System: Confirm storage
    System-->>User: Confirm file sent

    User->>System: Request file
    System->>Media: Retrieve file
    Media-->>System: Return file
    System-->>User: Deliver file